}
```

This ranking prioritizes apps with:
- Comprehensive help centers and FAQ sections
- Multiple support channels (email, social media, forums)
- Active community moderation and response
- Regular updates addressing user concerns
- Strong presence on official support platforms
- Responsive customer service teams
- Well-documented troubleshooting resources
- Active engagement with user feedback

IMDb leads due to its extensive support infrastructure and Amazon backing, while Letterboxd and Rotten Tomatoes follow with strong community support and responsive teams.